snippet: Juergen Braehmer of Germany unanimously outpointed Roberto Feliciano Bolonti of Argentina to retain his WBA light heavyweight belt on Saturday....

headline.print_headline: Braehmer Outpoints Bolonti to Retain WBA Belt
headline.main: Braehmer Outpoints Bolonti to Retain WBA Belt

lead_paragraph: Juergen Braehmer of Germany unanimously outpointed Roberto Feliciano Bolonti of Argentina to retain his WBA light heavyweight belt on Saturday.
